high_descs: Turn to your right and go to the table on the left side of the kitchen, across the room.
Pick up the butter knife, between the spoon and the spatula, on the table.
Move over to the left side of the table.
Cut the apple to the right of the toaster, on the table, into slices.
Turn to your right and go to the right cabinet under the sink.
Place the knife in the front of the right cabinet, under the sink.
Turn to your left and go back to the table.
Pick up one of the apple slices.
Turn to your right and go to the sink.
Place the apple slice in the back, right corner of the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the apple slice, turn the water off, and remove the apple slice from the sink.
Turn to your right and go across the room to the garbage bin on the floor, to the left of the refrigerator.
Place the apple slice in the garbage bin.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple slice in the garbage bin.

high_descs: Turn around and move to the wood table across the room.
Pick up the butter knife from behind the salt shaker.
Move a step to the left while carrying the knife.
Use the knife to slice the apple that's next to the toaster.
Turn right to carry the knife to stand in front of the kitchen sink.
Open the left cupboard beneath the sink and place the knife inside.
Turn around again to move back to the table where you left the sliced apple.
Pick up the apple slice from the table.
Turn right and carry the apple slice to the sink.
Place the apple slice in the sink, turn on the water, and then remove it once rinsed.
Turn right and carry the apple slice to the wall and then turn right to face the trash bin next to the fridge.
Place the apple slice in the trash bin.
anns.task_desc: Throw away a washed slice of apple.
